Package com.google.closure.plugin.extract

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Extract
    Identifies an artifact to extract source files from.
    ExtractOptionPlanGraphNode
    An option set plan graph node that spawns nodes to resolve artifact names.
    ExtractPlanner
    Adds steps to the common plan to extract source files from specified dependencies' artifacts.
    Extracts
    Specify how to extract JS, CSS, Proto, and Soy dependencies from Maven artifacts.
    ResolvedExtractsList
    A list like Extracts.getExtracts() but after all the extracts have been resolved against the project's actual dependencies.
    ResolvedExtractsList.ResolvedExtract
    Like Extract but with all the optional parts filled in.
